Fayraska waxaa sidoo kale lagu faafi karaa marka qofku taabto dusha la wasakhaystay, oo ay ku jirto maqaarka, ka dibna uu taabto indhaha, sanka ama afka.
Inkastoo ay jirto walaac ah in fayraska uu ku faafi karo faaruqa, khatarta ayaa la rumeysan yahay inay hooseyso.
Dowladda Shiinaha ayaa diiday in ay suurtagal tahay in SARS-CoV-2 afka laga qaado. Fayraska ayaa ugu faafa saddexda maalmood ee ugu horeysa ee laga bilaabo bilowga calaamadaha, laakiin waxaa laga yaabaa in cudurku uu dhaco ka hor calaamadaha iyo marxaladaha dambe ee cudurka.
Dadka ayaa laga helay cudurka ilaa saddex maalmood ka hor bilowga calaamadaha, taas oo muujineysa in cudurku uu dhici karo ka hor inta aan calaamadaha la arki karin.
