Daraasad lagu barbardhigay PCR iyo CT ee Wuhan ayaa soo jeedisay in CT ay aad uga xasaasi badan tahay PCR, inkasta oo ay ka yar tahay takhasuska, iyadoo astaamaha muuqaalkooda badankood ay isku dhafan yihiin nidaamka sambabada iyo cudurrada kale.
Ilaa Maarso 2020, Kulliyadda Ruushka ee Radiology waxay ku talineysaa in "CT aan loo isticmaalin si loo shaandheeyo ama baaritaanka ugu horreeya ee lagu ogaado COVID-19".
