Falanqaynta qaabka safarka hawada ayaa loo adeegsaday in lagu muujiyo loona saadaaliyo qaabka faafitaanka waxaana lagu daabacay The Journal of Travel Medicine bartamihii Janaayo 2020.
Iyada oo ku saleysan xogta 2018 ee Ururka Caalamiga ah ee Gaadiidka Cirka, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, iyo Taipei waxay leeyihiin tirada ugu badan ee dalxiisayaasha ka yimid Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney, iyo Melbourne ayaa sidoo kale la sheegay inay yihiin meelo caan ku ah dadka ka imanaya Wuhan.
Bali ayaa lagu soo warramay inay tahay tan ugu liita 20ka magaalo ee ugu caansan marka loo eego helitaanka, halka magaalooyinka Australia ay yihiin kuwa ugu awooda badan.Australia waxay soo saartay Qorshaha Jawaabta Degdega ah ee Coronavirus (COVID-19) Febraayo 7.
Waxaa la sheegay in ay jiraan waxyaabo badan oo aan la ogeyn oo ku saabsan COVID-19, iyo in Australia ay xoojin doonto xakamaynta xuduudaha iyo isgaarsiinta jawaabta cudurka faafa.
21-kii Maarso, xaalad degdeg ah oo badbaadada bini'aadamka ah ayaa lagu dhawaaqay Australia.
Iyada oo la eegayo hirgelinta karantiil gaadiidka dadweynaha ee Wuhan iyo Hubei, dalal badan ayaa qorsheynaya inay ka soo saaraan muwaadiniintooda iyo shaqaalaha diblomaasiyadeed ee aagaggaas, guud ahaan duulimaadyo ay kireystaan dalalka ay ka yimaadeen, iyadoo ay oggolaansho siiyeen mas'uuliyiinta Shiinaha.
Canada, Maraykanka, Hindiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransiiska, Argentina, Jarmalka, iyo Thailand ayaa ka mid ah dalalkii ugu horeeyay ee qorsheynaya inay dadka ka soo saaraan.
Pakistan waxay sheegtay inaysan ka soo saari doonin dadkeeda Shiinaha.
Bishii Febraayo 7, Brazil waxay ka soo daadgureysay 34 muwaadin oo reer Brazil ah ama xubnaha qoysaskooda marka lagu daro afar muwaadin oo reer Poland ah, hal muwaadin oo Shiine ah, iyo hal muwaadin oo Hindi ah.
Dadka reer Poland, Shiinaha, iyo Hindiya ayaa laga soo dejiyey Poland, halkaasoo diyaaraddii Brazil ay joogsatay ka hor inta aysan sii wadin safarkeeda Brazil.
Muwaadiniinta Brazil ee tagaya Wuhan ayaa lagu karantiilay saldhig ciidan oo ku dhow Brasilia.
Isla maalintaas, 215 muwaadin oo reer Kanada ah (176 qof oo ka soo duulay diyaaraddii koowaad, iyo 39 qof oo ka soo duulay diyaaraddii labaad ee ay kireysatay dowladda Mareykanka) ayaa laga soo qaaday Wuhan kuna wareejiyay CFB Trenton si loo karantiilo laba toddobaad.
11-kii Febraayo, diyaarad kale oo wata 185 qof oo reer Kanada ah oo ka timid Wuhan ayaa ka degtay saldhigga CFB ee Trenton.
Mas'uuliyiinta Australia ayaa 277 qof u wareejiyay 3 iyo 4 Febraayo Xarunta Xadhiga ee Jasiiradda Christmas, oo loo beddelay xarun karantiil, halkaas oo ay ku noolaayeen 14 maalmood.
Diyaarad ka timid New Zealand ayaa gaadhay Aukland 5-tii Febraayo; rakaabkeedii (oo ay ku jiraan qaar ka mid ah dadka Australia iyo Baasifigga) ayaa la karantiilay saldhigga badda ee Whangaparoa, waqooyiga Aukland.
15-kii Febraayo, Mareykanka ayaa ku dhawaaqay in uu u wareejin doono dadka Mareykanka ah markabka Diamond Princess.
21 Febraayo, diyaarad ay la socdeen 129 qof oo reer Canada ah oo laga soo daadgureeyay Diamond Princess ayaa ka degtay Trento, Ontario.
Bilowgii bishii Maarso, dowladda Hindiya ayaa bilaabay inay dadkeeda ka soo daadgureyso Iiraan. 14-kii Maarso diyaarad ay leedahay South African Airways oo ay kireysatay dowladda Koonfur Afrika ayaa dib ugu soo celisay 112 qof oo reer Koonfur Afrika ah.
Baaritaanka caafimaadka ayaa la sameeyay ka hor intaan la sii deyn, afar qof oo reer Koonfur Afrika ah oo muujinaya calaamadaha coronavirus ayaa la daayay si loo yareeyo halista.
Kaliya dadka Koonfur Afrika ee baaritaanka lagu sameeyay ee diidmada leh ayaa dib loogu celiyay.
Natiijooyinka baaritaanka ayaa xaqiijinaya in dhammaan dadka reer Koonfur Afrika, oo ay ku jiraan shaqaalaha duulimaadka, duuliyeyaasha, shaqaalaha hoteelka, booliska iyo ciidamada ku lug leh howlgalka bini'aadanimada kuwaas oo, si taxadar leh, dhammaantood loo dhigay kormeerka iyo karantiil 14 maalmood ah ee The Ranch Resort.
Bishii Maarso, Mareykanka wuxuu bilaabay in uu ka saaro qeyb ka mid ah ciidamadiisa Ciraaq sababtoo ah cudurka faafa.
5-tii Febraayo, Wasaaradda Arrimaha Dibadda ee Shiinaha ayaa sheegtay in 21 dal (oo ay ku jiraan Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad iyo Tobago, Masar iyo Iran) ay gargaar u direen Shiinaha.
Ardayda Shiinaha ee jaamacadaha Mareykanka ayaa isku duubay si ay u caawiyaan gaarsiinta gargaarka aagagga ay ku dhacday fayraska ee Shiinaha, iyadoo kooxo wadajir ah oo ku nool aagga weyn ee Chicago ay soo warrameen inay ku guuleysteen inay 50,000 oo maaskaro N95 ah u diraan isbitaal ku yaal gobolka Hubei Janaayo 30.Hay'adda gargaarka bani'aadamnimada ee Direct Relief, oo la kaashanaysa FedEx, waxay 200,000 oo maaskaro ah iyo qalab kale oo ilaalin shaqsiyeed ah u direen, oo ay ku jiraan galoofyo iyo dhar, iyada oo loo marayo gaarsiinta degdegga ah ee hawada ee Isbitaalka Ururka Wuhan Janaayo 30.
Bishii Febraayo 5, Bill iyo Melinda Gates waxay ku dhawaaqeen in ay $100 milyan oo doolar ugu deeqeen WHO si ay u maalgeliyaan cilmi baarista tallaalka iyo dadaallada daaweynta si wadajir ah loo ilaaliyo "dadka halista ku jira ee Afrika iyo Koonfurta Aasiya".
Isku-xirnaanta ayaa soo warisay in dowladda Shiinaha ay 200,000 oo maaskaro ah ugu deeqday Filibiin Febraayo 6, ka dib markii Senator Richard Gordon uu 3.16 milyan oo maaskaro ah u diray Wuhan.
Bishii Febraayo 19, Laanqeyrta Cas ee Singapore ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay Shiinaha u dirayso $2.26 milyan oo gargaar ah.
Japan ayaa Wuhan ugu deeqday hal milyan oo maaskaro ah, Turkiga ayaa u diray qalab caafimaad, Ruushka ayaa Wuhan u diray in ka badan 13 tan oo sahay caafimaad ah, Malaysia ayaa ku dhawaaqday in ay Shiinaha ugu deeqday 18 milyan oo galoof caafimaad, Jarmalka ayaa Shiinaha u diray sahay caafimaad oo kala duwan oo ay ku jiraan 10,000 oo dhar oo khatar ah, Mareykanka ayaa Shiinaha ugu deeqay 17.8 tan oo gargaar caafimaad ah waxayna ballanqaadeen in ay $100 milyan oo dheeraad ah oo lacag ah ugu deeqaan dalalka ay saameysay. Kadib markii kiisaska Shiinaha ay si tartiib tartiib ah u degsadeen, dalka ayaa gargaar u diray dalal badan oo ay saameysay cudurka faafa.
Bishii Maarso, Shiinaha, Cuba iyo Ruushka ayaa u diray gargaar caafimaad iyo khabiiro si ay uga caawiyaan Talyaaniga xakamaynta cudurka faafa ee coronavirus.
Ganacsade Jack Ma ayaa 1.1 milyan oo qalab baaritaan ah, 6 milyan oo maaskaro wajiga ah, iyo 60,000 oo dhar ilaalin ah u diray Addis Ababa, Ethiopia si ay u qaybiyaan Midowga Afrika.
Kadib wuxuu Panama u diray 5,000 oo qalab baaritaan ah, 100,000 oo maaskaro wajiga ah iyo 5 qalab neefsashada.
Ma ayaa sidoo kale deeq caafimaad u diray Kanada, Holland, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, iyo Czech Republic ayaa muujisay walaac ay ka qabaan maaskaro iyo qalab baaritaan oo Shiinaha laga sameeyay.
Tusaale ahaan, Spain waxay dib u soo celineysaa 58,000 oo xirmo baaritaan oo Shiinaha lagu sameeyay oo lagu baaray coronavirus oo leh heerka saxnimada 30%, halka Nederland ay dib u soo celineyso 600,000 oo waji-xidhayaal Shiinaha ah oo waxyeeloobay.
Belgium ayaa dib ugu soo celineysa 100,000 oo maaskaro waji oo aan la isticmaali karin, oo loo maleynayo inay ka yimaadeen Shiinaha, laakiin dhab ahaantii waxay ka yimaadeen Colombia.
Dhanka kale, gargaarka Shiinaha ayaa si wanaagsan loogu soo dhaweeyay qaybo ka mid ah Latin America iyo Afrika.
WHO ayaa bogaadisay dadaalka ay dowladda Shiinaha ku sameyneyso xakamaynta cudurka faafa.
WHO waxay ka duwanaantahay cudurka faafa ee SARS ee 2002-2004, markii dowladda Shiinaha lagu eedeeyay inay qarsoodi tahay si ay u saameyso dadaallada ka hortagga iyo xakamaynta, iyo xiisadda hadda jirta ee aragtay dowladda dhexe "oo si joogto ah u soo bandhigtay warbixinno si looga fogaado cabsida ka hor fasaxyada Sannadka Cusub ee Shiinaha".
23kii Janaayo, iyadoo ka jawaabtay go'aanka dowladda dhexe ee lagu soo rogay xannibaadaha gaadiidka ee Wuhan, wakiilka WHO Gauden Galea wuxuu sheegay in inkasta oo "ay tahay in aysan ahayn talo soo jeedin ay soo saartay WHO", haddana ay tahay "tusaale aad muhiim u ah sida loo go'aamiyo in la xakameeyo cudurka faafa halka uu aad ugu xooggan yahay" wuxuuna ku tilmaamay "aan horay loo arag taariikhda caafimaadka dadweynaha". 30kii Janaayo, ka dib xaqiijinta faafitaanka bini'aadamka ee bini'aadamka ee ka baxsan Shiinaha iyo kororka tirada kiisaska dalalka kale, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday cudurka faafa inuu yahay Caafimaad Caafimaad oo Caafimaad ah oo heer caalami ah (PHEIC), PHEIC-da lixaad tan iyo markii tallaabada markii ugu horreysay la qaaday intii lagu jiray cudurka faafa ee doofaarka ee 2009.
Agaasimaha guud ee WHO Tedros Adhanom ayaa sheegay in PHEIC ay sabab u tahay "halista faafitaanka caalamiga ah gaar ahaan dalalka dakhligoodu hooseeyo iyo kuwa dhexdhexaadka ah ee aan haysan nidaam caafimaad oo adag.
Isagoo ka jawaabaya hirgelinta xayiraadaha safarka, Tedros wuxuu sheegay in "aan jirin sabab loo qaato tallaabooyin si aan loo baahnayn u carqaladeynaya safarka iyo ganacsiga caalamiga ah" iyo "WHO ma talineyso in la xaddido ganacsiga iyo dhaqdhaqaaqa".
5-tii Febraayo, WHO waxay ugu baaqday beesha caalamka inay deeq u soo dirto $675 milyan oo doolar si ay u maalgashato diyaar garowga istiraatiijiyadeed ee wadamada dakhligoodu hooseeyo, iyadoo sheegtay muhiimadda ay leedahay in la taageero wadamadaas oo "aan haysan nidaam la heli karo si loo ogaado dadka uu ku dhacay fayraska, haddii uu soo baxo".
Tedros ayaa hadalkiisa sii wata ku dhawaaqay in "anu nahay kuwa ugu xoogga badan ee silsiladdeena ugu daciifsan" wuxuuna ugu baaqay beesha caalamka inay "maalgashadaan maanta ama ay dib u bixiyaan". 11-kii Febraayo, WHO waxay shir jaraa'id ku qabatay COVID-19 oo ah magaca cudurka.
Isla maalintaas, Tedros wuxuu sheegay in xoghayaha guud ee Qaramada Midoobay Antonio Guterres uu ku heshiiyey inuu siiyo "awoodda nidaamka Qaramada Midoobay oo dhan jawaab celin".
Natiijo ahaan kooxda Maareynta Xasaradaha ee Qaramada Midoobay ayaa la hawlgeliyay, taas oo u oggolaanaysa in la isku hagaajiyo jawaabta guud ee Qaramada Midoobay, taas oo WHO ay sheegtay inay u oggolaan doonto inay " diirada saaraan jawaabta caafimaadka halka hay'adaha kale ay keeni karaan khibradooda si ay ula qabsadaan saameynta xun ee ballaaran ee bulshada, dhaqaalaha iyo horumarka ee cudurka faafa".
Bishii Febraayo 14, Kooxda Wadajirka ah ee Shiinaha ee WHO ay hogaaminayso ayaa loo hawlgeliyay inay siiso khibrad caalami ah iyo WHO oo ku sugan dhulka Shiinaha si ay uga caawiyaan maaraynta gudaha iyo qiimeynta "dhibka iyo faafa ee cudurka" iyagoo qabtay aqoon isweydaarsiyo iyo kulamo la leh hay'adaha heer qaranka ah ee waaweyn iyo booqasho booqasho ah si loo qiimeeyo "saameynta waxqabadka jawaabta ee heer gobol iyo tuulo, oo ay ku jiraan deegaannada magaalooyinka iyo miyiga".Bishii Febraayo 25, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday in "adduunku ay tahay inuu sameeyo wax badan si uu u diyaariyo cudurka faafa ee coronavirus" iyadoo sheegtay in inkasta oo ay weli tahay mid aad u horeysa in la yiraahdo cudurka faafa, dalalku ay tahay inay "ku jiraan marxaladda diyaarinta".
Iyada oo laga jawaabayo cudurka faafa ee ka socda Iran, WHO waxay u dirtay Kooxda Hawlaha Wadajirka ah si ay u qiimeeyaan xaaladda.Bishii Febraayo 28, saraakiisha WHO ayaa sheegay in qiimeynta halista caalamiga ah ee coronavirus laga kordhin doono "sare" ilaa "ugu sarreeya", heerka ugu sarreeya ee digniinta iyo qiimeynta halista.
Mike Ryan, agaasimaha fulinta ee barnaamijka caafimaadka degdegga ah ee WHO, ayaa ka digay bayaan uu soo saaray in "Tani ay tahay dib u eegis xaqiiqo ah oo loogu talagalay dowlad kasta oo ku taal meeraha inix: Kac.
Fayrasku wuxuu noqon karaa mid socda waana inaad diyaar u ahaataa, "isagoo ku nuuxnuuxsaday in tallaabooyinka jawaabta saxda ah ay caawiyaan adduunka inuu ka fogaado "xaaladaha ugu xun".
Ryan ayaa intaas ku daray in xogta hadda jirta aysan u oggolaanayn saraakiisha caafimaadka guud inay ku dhawaaqaan cudur faafa oo caalami ah, sidaa darteedna ku dhawaaqa ayaa macnaheedu yahay "waxaan si aasaasi ah u aqbalnaa in dhammaan dadka dhulka jooga ay u nugul yihiin fayraska".
11-kii Maarso, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday in cudurka faafa ee coronavirus uu yahay cudur faafa.
Agaasimaha guud ayaa sheegay in WHO ay "si weyn uga walaacsan tahay heerarka faafitaanka iyo halista ah ee walaacsan, iyo heerarka aan la shaqeyn ee walaacsan". WHO waxay la kulantay dhaliilo aad u weyn oo ku saabsan waxa loo arko inay tahay maaraynta cudurka faafa ee aan habooneyn, oo ay ku jiraan dib u dhaca ku yimaada ku dhawaaqista xaalad caafimaad oo degdeg ah iyo kala soocida fayraska cudurka faafa.
Cambaareynta ayaa waxaa ka mid ah codsi uu ku baaqay Agaasimaha Guud ee WHO Tedros Adhanom inuu is casilo, oo ay saxiixeen 733,000 oo qof illaa iyo 6-dii Abriil.
26 Maarso 2020, daraasiin khabiir oo ka tirsan hay'adda xuquuqda aadanaha ee Qaramada Midoobay ayaa carabka ku adkeeyay xuquuqda shaqsiga ee qof walba inta lagu jiro cudurka faafa ee COVID-19.
Kooxda khabiirada ayaa sheegtay in qof walba uu xaq u leeyahay inuu helo faragelin badbaadinaysa nolol iyo in dowladaha ay leeyihiin masuuliyadaas.
Kooxda ayaa carrabka ku adkeysay in la'aanta ilaha ama caymiska caafimaadka aysan ahayn sabab loo takooro koox gaar ah.
Khubaradu waxay tilmaamayaan in qof walba uu xaq u leeyahay caafimaad, oo ay ku jiraan dadka naafada ah, xubnaha kooxaha yaryar, waayeelka, dadka barakacayaasha ah, kuwa aan guryaha lahayn, kuwa ku nool xaaladaha aadka u adag, maxaabiista, iyo sidoo kale qaxootiga iyo kooxaha kale ee u baahan caawimaadda dowladda.
Ururada dowladaha caalamiga ah ayaa ka hadlaya saameynta dhaqaale iyo bulshada ee xiisadda COVID-19.
Ururka Iskaashiga Dhaqaalaha iyo Horumarinta ayaa bilaabay barxad si loo siiyo macluumaad waqtigeeda ku habboon oo dhammaystiran oo ku saabsan jawaab celinta siyaasadeed ee dalalka adduunka oo dhan, iyo sidoo kale aragtiyo iyo talooyin.
Laga soo bilaabo siyaasadaha lagu xoojinayo nidaamyada caafimaadka iyo dhaqaalaha adduunka ilaa ka wada hadalka saameynta xaaladaha degdegga ah iyo xayiraadaha safarka, xarunta dhijitaalka ah waxaa ka mid ah Raadinta Siyaasadaha Qaranka, waxayna ujeedkeedu yahay inay ka caawiso waddamada inay ka bartaan midba midka kale iyo fududeynta jawaab isku dhafan oo caalami ah oo ku saabsan caqabadaha coronavirus.
Dowladda Shiinaha ayaa waxaa dhaliilay Mareykanka, Wasiirka Wasaaradda Xukuumadda ee UK Michael Gove iyo wiilkii Madaxweynaha Brazil Jair Bolsonaro ee Eduardo Bolsonaro kadib xakamaynta cudurka faafa, oo ka bilaabatay gobolka Hubei ee Shiinaha.
Qaar ka mid ah saraakiisha heer gobol ee Xisbiga Shuuciga Shiinaha (CPC) ayaa la eryay sababtoo ah sida loo maareeyo karantiilka bartamaha Shiinaha, iyagoo muujinaya niyad jab ka dhan ah jawaabta ururada siyaasadeed ee cudurka ku faafay gobolka.
Qaar ka mid ah faallooyinka ayaa aaminsan in tallaabadan ay tahay mid loogu talagalay in lagu ilaaliyo Xoghayaha Guud ee Xisbiga Shuuciga Shiinaha Xi Jinping cadhada bulshada ee faafitaanka coronavirus.
Saraakiil badan oo Shiinees ah, oo uu ka mid yahay Zhao Lijian ayaa diiday warbixinnadii hore ee sheegaya in cudurka coronavirus uu ka bilaabmay Wuhan, iyagoo ku raacay aragtida shirqoolka ah ee ah in COVID-19 uu ka yimid Mareykanka ama Talyaaniga.
Maamulka Mareykanka ee Donald Trump ayaa u gudbiyay coronavirus "virus-ka Shiinaha" ama "virus-ka Wuhan" isagoo sheegay in "Shiinaha uu soo saaray fayras hadda u noqday cudur faafa oo caalami ah", kaas oo markii dambe qaar ka mid ah dhaleeceeyayaasha ay ku dhaleeceyeen inuu yahay mid cunsuriyad leh oo "isku dayaya inuu diiradda ka leexdo guuldarada maamulkiisa ee xakameynta cudurka".
Daily Beast waxay heshay warbixin ka timid dowladda Mareykanka oo muujineysa in farsamooyinka isgaarsiinta ay asal ahaan ka yimaadeen Golaha Ammaanka Qaranka, iyadoo istaraatijiyaddan lagu tilmaamay "Wax walba waxay ku saabsan yihiin Shiinaha.
Waxaa naloo sheegay inaan isku dayno oo aan hubinno in fariintan la soo bandhigo si kasta oo ay suurtagal tahay, oo ay ku jiraan shirarka warbaahinta iyo muuqaalada telefishanka. "Wararka sida Politico, Foreign Policy iyo Bloomberg ayaa sheeganaya in dadaalka Shiinaha ee ah inuu gargaar u diro dalalka uu ku dhacay fayraska uu qayb ka yahay dadaal been abuur ah oo lagu saameynayo adduunka.
Madaxa siyaasadda dibadda ee Midowga Yurub Josep Borrell ayaa ka digay in ay jirto "qayb geo-siyaasadeed oo ay ku jiraan halganka saameynta lagu helo wareegga iyo 'siyaasadda deeqsinimada'.
Borrell wuxuu kaloo yiri "Shiinaha wuxuu si xoog leh u dhiirrigeliyaa fariinta ah in, si ka duwan Mareykanka, uu yahay saaxiib mas'uul ah oo lagu kalsoonaan karo".
Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale ku booriyay Mareykanka inuu ka qaado xayiraadihii uu ku soo rogay Suuriya, Venezuela iyo Iran, iyadoo la sheegay inay gargaar u dirtay labada dal ee ugu dambeeyay.
Deeqda 100,000 oo maaskaro ah oo Jack Ma uu u diray Cuba ayaa waxaa xannibay cunaqabateyntii Mareykanka ee 3-dii Abriil.
Masuuliyiinta Mareykanka ayaa sidoo kale lagu eedeeyay inay gargaar u dirayaan dalal kale si ay dalkooda ugu soo galaan.
Waxaa jira khilaafaadyo la xiriira maaskaro oo la sheegay in ay ka dhaceen dalal kale, sida Jarmalka, Austria iyo Switzerland; iyo Czech Republic iyo Italy.
Intaa waxaa dheer, Turkiga ayaa qabsaday boqolaal qalab oo neefsashada ah oo u socda Spain.
Bilowgii Maarso, dowladda Talyaaniga ayaa dhaliishay in Midowga Yurub uu la'yahay midnimo la'aan Talyaaniga oo ay saameysay cudurka coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, safiirka Talyaaniga ee Midowga Yurub, ayaa yiri "Shiinaha ayaa kaliya ka jawaabaya labada dhinac.
Xaqiiqdii, tani ma aha calaamad wanaagsan oo ku saabsan wadajirka Yurub".
22kii Maarso, kadib wicitaan telefoon oo uu la yeeshay Ra'iisul Wasaaraha Talyaaniga Giuseppe Conte, Madaxweynaha Ruushka Vladimir Putin ayaa ku amray ciidamada Ruushka inay u diraan ciidamo caafimaad oo ciidan, gawaarida qaboojiyaha gaarka ah iyo qalab kale oo caafimaad Talyaaniga.
Wargeyska Talyaaniga ee La Stampa ayaa soo xigtay "ilaha siyaasadeed ee heerka sare ah" oo aan magacyadooda sheegin oo sheegay in 80 boqolkiiba gargaarka Ruushka uu yahay "wax aan faa'iido lahayn ama wax yar u tarayn Talyaaniga".
Ilo wareedyo ayaa ku eedeeyay Ruushka inay ku xadgudbeen "jiopolitikada iyo diblomaasiyadda".
Madaxweynaha gobolka Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, iyo wasiirka arrimaha dibada Talyaaniga Luigi Di Maio ayaa diiday wararka warbaahinta waxayna muujiyeen mahadnaq.
Ruushka ayaa sidoo kale diyaarad caafimaad u diray Maraykanka.
Afhayeenka Kremlin Dmitry Peskov ayaa sheegay in "markuu caawimaad u fidiyay saaxiibbadiis Mareykanka, [Putin] uu u maleynayay in marka soo saarayaasha qalabka caafimaadka iyo alaabada Mareykanka ay helaan dhaqdhaqaaq, ay sidoo kale awoodi doonaan inay ka jawaabaan haddii loo baahdo".
